// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1933 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 47962f24-2440-5d85-a360-91589ad9e5bd

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04-ESM*")
